Burmah oil PLC, one British independent oil, and specialty chemical marketing concern, na im talk sey dis one wey be sey de don build up na 7.5% stake for di company.

Di holding of 13.6 million shares dey up from di 6.7% stake wey Burmah announce on top of last Monday.

WHETHER na di Netherlands wey join di North Sea oil, gas operation with Calor Group PLC wey get 40% of Calor, dem come identify am as possible suitor for Burmah.

Burmah say no be matter of size na matter of size o.

